{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">知道全反射的概念及发生全反射的条件；观察全反射现象。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光从光密介质射入到光疏介质时，当入射角等于或者大于临界角时，会发生全反射现象</span><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">激光笔、半圆玻璃、量角器</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.拖动激光笔，使激光沿着半圆形玻璃砖的半径射到它的平直的边上；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.逐渐增大入射角，观察反射光线和折射光线的变化。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">当入射角增大到某一角度时，使折射角达到</span>90<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&deg;时，折射光完全消失，只剩下反射光，就能发生全反射；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光从光密介质射入到光疏介质时，当入射角等于或者大于临界角时，才会发生全反射现象</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光从介质射入空气（真空）时，发生全反射的临界角</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">C</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与介质的折射率</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>n</em></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的关系是：<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">sinC=1/<em>n</em></span>。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}